WEBVTT

00:15.430 --> 00:19.930
ظآزDuring the dark nightظآز

00:20.100 --> 00:22.730
ظآزA guiding lightظآز

00:23.230 --> 00:25.000
ظآزJust like youظآز

00:25.430 --> 00:29.700
ظآزMakes life turn brightظآز

00:30.300 --> 00:35.130
ظآزBreaking free from darknessظآز

00:35.400 --> 00:38.870
ظآزYou gave me strengthظآز

00:39.200 --> 00:41.730
ظآزRunning for truthظآز

00:41.800 --> 00:45.830
ظآزI find my pathظآز

00:46.600 --> 00:50.570
ظآزDrawing on the hopeظآز

00:51.200 --> 00:54.570
ظآزThat you render meظآز

00:55.100 --> 00:57.970
ظآزIn this long journeyظآز

00:58.230 --> 01:01.630
ظآزI run on lightlyظآز

01:19.170 --> 01:22.970
[Reborn]
[Adapted from Qiang Yu's work, Reborn]

01:25.400 --> 01:26.800
The makeup needs a quick fix.

01:26.870 --> 01:28.100
The ceremony is about to start.

01:29.330 --> 01:30.930
Let's try a peach blossom color
on your makeup.

01:30.970 --> 01:31.500
Hmm.

01:36.130 --> 01:36.800
Where are her bridal shoes?

01:39.530 --> 01:40.570
Don't tell me they were left in the car.

01:41.670 --> 01:42.570
The car is parked
at the village entrance.

01:42.900 --> 01:44.100
Never mind. I'll take you there.

01:44.100 --> 01:44.800
You might get lost.

01:44.930 --> 01:45.229
Okay.

01:49.670 --> 01:50.170
Qingyu.

01:50.470 --> 01:50.970
Could you

01:50.970 --> 01:51.830
straighten

01:51.830 --> 01:52.830
Xiaoyun's dress hem

01:53.000 --> 01:54.400
and help her put on this pendant?

01:54.729 --> 01:55.170
I'll leave it here.

02:01.670 --> 02:02.900
I'm counting on you today.

02:06.170 --> 02:07.470
Xiaoyun.

02:08.400 --> 02:10.570
How did you meet Jinrui?

02:12.630 --> 02:14.130
I was in my third year of university.

02:15.000 --> 02:17.200
Jinrui invited me to star
in a short film

02:17.200 --> 02:18.130
for the movie club.

02:19.000 --> 02:20.630
He was the male lead.

02:20.930 --> 02:22.400
I was the female lead.

02:23.030 --> 02:23.870
What are the odds?

02:23.900 --> 02:25.770
We were a couple in the film.

02:26.270 --> 02:27.900
Back then, I played

02:27.900 --> 02:29.170
a girl who was great at dancing.

02:30.570 --> 02:31.829
After the movie wrapped up,

02:32.200 --> 02:34.000
we got closer over time.

02:34.470 --> 02:36.500
And soon enough, we fell in love.

02:36.829 --> 02:38.000
We became a real couple.

02:40.100 --> 02:43.030
What was the short film about?

02:43.329 --> 02:45.200
It was a tragic love story.

02:45.930 --> 02:47.800
The two protagonists
didn't end up together.

02:48.829 --> 02:51.370
Maybe Jinrui found it was a bit unlucky,

02:51.770 --> 02:53.800
so he hid all the tapes away

02:53.800 --> 02:54.730
afterward.

02:55.270 --> 02:56.600
He wouldn't play them.

02:57.000 --> 02:57.870
However,

02:58.130 --> 03:00.430
I think fiction is not real life.

03:00.770 --> 03:02.630
See? Things worked out well for us.

03:02.900 --> 03:03.830
We're getting married.

03:08.170 --> 03:09.030
Sorry.

03:11.070 --> 03:16.030
[Episode 11]
[The Broken Wedding]

03:23.570 --> 03:24.530
Have you seen Qingyu?

03:25.030 --> 03:26.670
I saw her upstairs,

03:26.670 --> 03:27.770
helping Xiaoyun with her makeup.

03:30.930 --> 03:31.600
Leave it here.

03:32.000 --> 03:32.500
Sure.

03:32.530 --> 03:33.800
Does it look better this way?

03:33.970 --> 03:34.430
Yes.

03:35.100 --> 03:36.400
It looks wonderful.

03:43.270 --> 03:45.100
I jabbed my finger just now.

03:45.370 --> 03:46.770
It must have smudged your dress.

03:46.770 --> 03:47.630
How is your hand, Qingyu?

03:47.670 --> 03:48.270
I am alright.

03:51.670 --> 03:54.400
It's okay.
The smudge will come right off.

03:56.370 --> 03:58.670
The smudge on the dress can be erased,

03:59.430 --> 04:01.300
but a tarnished past stays forever.

04:02.800 --> 04:03.400
Come again?

04:05.830 --> 04:07.030
Xiaoyun.

04:09.830 --> 04:11.430
I wish you all the happiness.

04:13.370 --> 04:14.100
Hmm.

04:33.570 --> 04:34.400
Pull yourself together.

04:39.630 --> 04:40.230
Here.

04:41.300 --> 04:43.200
Your dad gave it to me

04:43.470 --> 04:44.470
when we got married.

04:45.430 --> 04:46.700
It's the only valuable gift I got.

04:47.270 --> 04:48.800
You are with the bride today.

04:49.670 --> 04:51.100
Make sure you look pretty today.

04:51.670 --> 04:52.530
Put this on later.

04:55.370 --> 04:56.500
After this wedding,

04:56.670 --> 04:58.170
we'll head back to Huanzhou.

04:58.870 --> 05:00.870
Leave all the unpleasant memories
in the past.

05:01.400 --> 05:03.270
You can't dwell on the past forever.

05:05.270 --> 05:06.070
Be happy.

05:24.370 --> 05:26.030
Jinrui.

05:26.630 --> 05:27.570
Look who's here.

05:27.600 --> 05:28.100
Jinrui!

05:28.400 --> 05:29.100
Long time no see.

05:29.230 --> 05:30.230
Congratulations, Jinrui.

05:30.670 --> 05:32.200
You two look like
a match made in heaven.

05:32.630 --> 05:33.130
Thank you.

05:33.300 --> 05:35.700
Jinrui, congratulations
on your marriage.

05:35.970 --> 05:37.400
I bet you'll be wrapped
around her finger soon.

05:37.870 --> 05:38.730
Ignore him.

05:38.970 --> 05:40.430
He is teasing you

05:40.430 --> 05:41.630
only because he can't
get a wife himself.

05:42.500 --> 05:43.200
Go on, take a seat.

05:43.430 --> 05:44.730
We've saved you two seats.

05:44.770 --> 05:45.800
Okay. We'll be over there.

05:47.500 --> 05:49.200
Didn't you invite the other classmates?

05:49.830 --> 05:51.330
Xiaoyun's parents told us

05:51.570 --> 05:52.430
they wanted a discreet wedding.

05:53.430 --> 05:54.730
We'll have another wedding on a trip.

06:00.870 --> 06:02.200
Feihai, come over here.

06:02.230 --> 06:02.930
I'll be over there.

06:04.300 --> 06:05.200
Here. This is for you.

06:05.900 --> 06:06.370
Anything else?

06:09.200 --> 06:09.730
Qing.

06:09.900 --> 06:11.430
Great timing.
Could you get another crate of sweets?

06:12.100 --> 06:13.930
Uncle Zhang, welcome. Long time no see.

06:14.230 --> 06:15.570
Mom and Dad, Uncle Zhang is here.

06:15.600 --> 06:16.800
The wedding sweets are coming.

06:24.430 --> 06:25.570
Thank you.

06:26.870 --> 06:28.070
Thank you so much.

06:35.470 --> 06:36.670
After this wedding,

06:37.030 --> 06:38.700
we'll head back to Huanzhou.

06:39.770 --> 06:42.230
Leave all the unpleasant memories
in the past.

06:42.800 --> 06:44.500
You can't dwell on the past forever.

06:55.200 --> 06:55.930
Qing.

06:56.270 --> 06:57.970
Don't just stand there.
We need the sweets.

06:58.230 --> 06:58.930
Qiao Huan.

06:59.470 --> 07:00.530
The box isn't full.

07:00.570 --> 07:01.700
Take this box instead.

07:02.230 --> 07:02.670
Okay.

07:03.070 --> 07:03.700
Welcome!

07:04.200 --> 07:04.900
Congratulations.

07:05.400 --> 07:06.530
Thank you for coming

07:06.570 --> 07:07.870
all the way here.

07:08.030 --> 07:09.500
Hope you enjoy yourself.

07:09.800 --> 07:10.430
Thanks, I will.

07:11.300 --> 07:15.200
We're thrilled to be here.

07:16.300 --> 07:17.000
Thank you.

07:17.770 --> 07:18.270
Mom and Dad,

07:18.470 --> 07:19.970
this is Mr. Liu, my team leader.

07:20.200 --> 07:21.800
He is performing well in the department.

07:21.800 --> 07:23.030
He's a diligent young man.

07:23.600 --> 07:24.930
All thanks to your guidance.

07:25.070 --> 07:25.770
Not at all.

07:25.830 --> 07:27.430
Mr. Liu has taken great care of me.

07:28.370 --> 07:29.270
Sorry for the trouble.

07:29.370 --> 07:30.600
It's my job.

07:50.100 --> 07:50.830
Thank you, Mr. Liu.

07:51.400 --> 07:52.600
Don't mention it.

07:52.670 --> 07:53.600
He is hardworking.

07:54.130 --> 07:54.900
Thank you, Mr. Liu.

07:54.970 --> 07:56.330
I hope he didn't cause any trouble.

07:56.370 --> 07:56.870
Not at all.

08:00.530 --> 08:02.030
How could Qiao Beiyu's family

08:02.030 --> 08:03.200
be here today?

08:03.570 --> 08:06.230
Yeah. Who knows what they are thinking?

08:06.230 --> 08:08.470
It's Jinrui's wedding reception.

08:09.000 --> 08:10.300
I wouldn't have invited them.

08:10.670 --> 08:12.700
They are nothing but trouble
for the Qiao family.

08:12.700 --> 08:13.330
Yeah.

08:13.400 --> 08:14.230
Jinrui shouldn't invite bad luck

08:14.670 --> 08:16.030
on his wedding day.

08:16.970 --> 08:18.370
The Qiao family is certainly unfortunate

08:18.400 --> 08:19.800
to have been involved with them.

08:19.800 --> 08:20.200
Indeed.

08:27.270 --> 08:30.100
May your children thrive and prosper.

08:30.530 --> 08:31.800
- Great!
- Great!

08:32.030 --> 08:34.770
May the bride be capable.

08:35.130 --> 08:36.330
- Great!
- Great!

08:36.600 --> 08:38.900
May they be wealthy!

08:39.370 --> 08:40.700
- Great!
- Great!

08:41.330 --> 08:43.870
May the loving couple be blessed
with brilliant children!

08:44.100 --> 08:46.130
I never asked them to raise my daughter.

08:46.930 --> 08:49.330
They took her away from me!

08:49.330 --> 08:51.830
Bow to Heaven and Earth.

08:54.400 --> 08:56.570
Jiangsheng, have you seen Qingyu?

08:56.570 --> 08:57.300
No.

08:57.330 --> 09:00.270
Bow to the parents.

09:00.730 --> 09:02.200
- Great!
- Great!

09:02.200 --> 09:05.100
Bow to each other.

09:06.170 --> 09:08.100
- Yeah!
- Yeah!

09:08.470 --> 09:08.970
Here.

09:09.230 --> 09:10.530
Remove the veil

09:10.570 --> 09:12.470
for the festive ceremony!

09:13.230 --> 09:16.670
Look at the gorgeous bride!

09:16.830 --> 09:18.900
- Great!
- Great!

09:19.100 --> 09:20.200
In times of helplessness,

09:20.330 --> 09:22.000
don a flower

09:22.600 --> 09:23.870
to vanquish evil.

09:24.930 --> 09:26.200
To tell the truth,

09:26.470 --> 09:27.570
change your pace.

09:28.330 --> 09:30.330
Prepare to set the towering trees ablaze.

09:30.800 --> 09:34.700
- Give her a kiss!
- Give her a kiss!

09:35.100 --> 09:36.400
A life unremembered

09:36.800 --> 09:38.270
is a life truly lost.

09:39.130 --> 09:40.630
But that doesn't mean

09:41.230 --> 09:44.030
a festive wedding is enough
to cover his unforgivable sins.

09:47.730 --> 09:49.030
Congratulations, Jinrui.

09:49.230 --> 09:51.130
Congratulations.

09:51.600 --> 09:52.670
Wishing you
a lifetime of happiness together.

10:06.000 --> 10:08.170
Take good care of the bride.

10:09.170 --> 10:10.470
What does this say?

10:10.470 --> 10:11.200
Have a baby soon.

10:11.230 --> 10:11.630
Sure.

10:14.470 --> 10:15.200
What is this?

10:27.700 --> 10:29.400
This man, a despicable coward

10:29.970 --> 10:31.570
who caused Beiyu's miscarriage

10:31.570 --> 10:32.670
and betrayed her,

10:33.700 --> 10:35.700
[The groom, Qiao Jinrui]
is the star of this event,

10:36.330 --> 10:37.430
the groom,

10:37.470 --> 10:38.630
Qiao Jinrui.

10:39.700 --> 10:42.870
The eldest grandson of the Qiao family
you're so proud of

10:43.400 --> 10:44.530
was adopted.

10:45.930 --> 10:47.930
To hide the truth,

10:48.230 --> 10:49.230
they smeared

10:49.230 --> 10:51.200
Beiyu's name

10:51.200 --> 10:51.870
and kept everyone in the dark.

10:51.870 --> 10:53.030
Six years ago,

10:53.070 --> 10:55.230
all the people of Nanqiao Village

10:55.230 --> 10:57.400
were murderers.

10:58.700 --> 11:01.030
The victim isn't allowed
to be buried with the family

11:01.070 --> 11:02.730
or to have a name.

11:03.230 --> 11:04.930
Qiao Beiyu.

11:06.000 --> 11:07.570
Were murderers.

11:08.100 --> 11:09.400
Six years ago...

11:09.400 --> 11:11.030
The victim isn't allowed
to be buried with the family

11:11.630 --> 11:14.070
or to have a name.

11:14.470 --> 11:16.100
The victim isn't allowed
to be buried with the family

11:16.130 --> 11:18.030
or to have a name.

11:18.070 --> 11:20.200
The victim isn't allowed
to be buried with the family

11:20.200 --> 11:22.070
or to have a name.

11:22.330 --> 11:23.630
Qiao Beiyu.

11:39.800 --> 11:42.200
You were trying to destroy Jinrui!

11:42.970 --> 11:44.800
Fine. All of you

11:45.730 --> 11:47.170
will pay for this!

11:47.170 --> 11:49.030
You will pay for this!

11:49.300 --> 11:50.600
Yanfen, calm down.

11:50.600 --> 11:52.270
What's done is done.

11:52.300 --> 11:52.800
Come.

11:53.630 --> 11:54.430
Yeah.

11:54.570 --> 11:55.870
Qingyu is missing.

11:55.870 --> 11:57.500
We should find her.

11:58.400 --> 11:59.570
What for?

11:59.830 --> 12:01.400
I hope she dies out there!

12:04.870 --> 12:07.330
Jinrui! My Jinrui!

12:09.570 --> 12:11.170
Jinrui!

12:11.330 --> 12:16.570
Jinrui! Why won't they let you
be happy for once?

12:19.130 --> 12:22.130
They've ruined you before.
Was that not enough?

12:22.230 --> 12:25.830
Do they have to destroy you for good?

12:25.830 --> 12:28.670
Jinrui! My Jinrui!

12:29.170 --> 12:30.900
Stand up. The floor is too cold.

12:34.930 --> 12:36.630
What a misfortune!

12:36.930 --> 12:38.270
Jinrui!

12:40.570 --> 12:45.270
[Cousin]

12:58.470 --> 13:01.170
[Cousin]

13:16.700 --> 13:22.600
[Get a job within the month.]

14:07.230 --> 14:07.970
Due to bad weather,

14:08.000 --> 14:10.570
the last bus tonight has been canceled.

14:10.700 --> 14:12.470
The earliest bus tomorrow

14:12.470 --> 14:13.670
is at 6:40 AM.

14:13.930 --> 14:15.330
I'll take that bus.

14:15.470 --> 14:16.400
All right. It's 98 yuan.

14:16.400 --> 14:17.200
Single unit with AC.

14:17.200 --> 14:18.270
It's at the entrance.

14:21.470 --> 14:22.230
Thank you.

14:24.470 --> 14:25.270
Accommodation?

14:34.530 --> 14:35.700
Miss, do you need accommodation?

14:35.700 --> 14:36.930
It's right outside the station.

14:37.000 --> 14:38.100
Single unit with AC.

14:38.170 --> 14:39.070
Normally, it's 160 yuan,

14:39.100 --> 14:39.770
but it's late,

14:39.770 --> 14:40.800
so it's 80 yuan.

14:40.970 --> 14:42.100
No, thanks.

14:42.130 --> 14:43.430
Miss, how about 70 yuan?

14:43.470 --> 14:44.570
Please show some support.

14:44.570 --> 14:45.100
Never mind.

14:45.130 --> 14:45.870
It's dangerous for a girl

14:45.870 --> 14:47.530
to be at the station alone at night.

16:44.600 --> 16:45.930
Excuse me.

16:46.200 --> 16:46.770
Hello.

16:46.770 --> 16:48.100
My wallet was stolen.

16:48.270 --> 16:49.300
When did that happen?

16:49.300 --> 16:50.170
How much did you lose?

16:50.200 --> 16:51.930
I was sleeping on that bench.

16:52.000 --> 16:53.770
It was gone when I woke up.

16:54.030 --> 16:56.070
What's your name? How old are you?

16:56.100 --> 16:56.730
I am...

16:57.030 --> 16:59.330
And the names and contacts
of your family members.

16:59.400 --> 17:00.200
And the ID numbers too.

17:00.430 --> 17:02.170
I'll write the situation down.

17:02.200 --> 17:04.400
It's best you file a report

17:04.400 --> 17:05.030
at the local police station.

17:05.099 --> 17:07.700
Sorry, maybe I was mistaken.

17:51.330 --> 17:53.570
[Dishwashers needed(all genders).
Free meals and room. Salary negotiable.]

18:06.570 --> 18:07.470
Madam?

18:08.100 --> 18:09.970
What would you like to order,
young lady?

18:10.330 --> 18:11.400
I'm not ordering.

18:11.830 --> 18:14.730
My wallet was stolen
at the train station.

18:14.730 --> 18:16.600
Could I borrow your phone?

18:21.870 --> 18:22.630
Thank you.

18:28.000 --> 18:31.300
The number you dialed is turned off.

18:37.030 --> 18:40.400
The number you dialed is turned off.

18:41.530 --> 18:42.570
No answer.

18:51.630 --> 18:53.730
[Vegetarian noodles, 6 yuan]

18:55.430 --> 18:57.130
Could I have a bowl
of vegetarian noodles?

18:57.200 --> 18:58.930
But I only have five yuan.

18:59.130 --> 19:00.870
I don't mind having less noodles.

19:22.030 --> 19:24.130
I didn't order the egg.
I can't afford it.

19:25.000 --> 19:26.670
Never mind. It's on the house.

19:34.330 --> 19:36.170
Go home when you're done.

19:36.670 --> 19:38.870
The world out here is dangerous.

19:39.030 --> 19:39.900
You can't tell

19:39.900 --> 19:41.470
who the good guys are

19:41.500 --> 19:42.900
by their appearances.

19:43.330 --> 19:45.170
It's not safe for a girl

19:45.770 --> 19:47.070
to spend the night outside.

19:59.470 --> 20:01.130
Did you finish it? Go home.

20:01.470 --> 20:02.330
Your family is worried.

20:03.200 --> 20:04.900
Home is the best, right?

20:05.300 --> 20:06.230
Madam.

20:08.300 --> 20:10.300
Could I stay and work part-time
for a few days?

20:10.330 --> 20:11.830
I can prepare the ingredients

20:11.870 --> 20:12.800
and cook the noodles.

20:12.800 --> 20:14.230
My family owns a noodle shop.

20:14.600 --> 20:16.430
I was going to Jiangzhou for work,

20:17.000 --> 20:19.270
but my ID and wallet

20:19.270 --> 20:20.370
got stolen.

20:20.700 --> 20:22.000
After I have enough for a ride,

20:22.070 --> 20:24.770
food, and phone calls, I'll leave.

20:28.500 --> 20:30.800
Fine. You can stay and work.

20:31.000 --> 20:31.670
Thank you.

21:10.500 --> 21:11.570
Hello. Where to?

21:11.570 --> 21:12.370
Sir.

21:13.000 --> 21:14.530
I need to go to Nanqiao Village
in Shunyun.

21:14.530 --> 21:16.530
All the way to Shunyun?

21:16.530 --> 21:17.170
Yeah.

21:17.330 --> 21:19.030
That's over 200 kilometers for one trip.

21:19.070 --> 21:20.470
Please hurry. It's urgent.

21:20.470 --> 21:20.970
Okay.

22:01.500 --> 22:03.730
Young lady, pick up the pace.

22:13.330 --> 22:15.830
Young lady, are you not feeling well?

22:17.330 --> 22:18.270
It's all right.

22:18.500 --> 22:21.000
You can deduct the amount from my pay.

22:21.100 --> 22:21.930
Young lady,

22:22.000 --> 22:23.430
I'd love to keep you here.

22:23.570 --> 22:25.270
Those hands are far too delicate

22:25.300 --> 22:26.500
for hard labor

22:26.500 --> 22:28.630
like dishwashing.

22:28.730 --> 22:30.600
You are meant to work in an office.

22:31.000 --> 22:32.670
It's best not to stay outside
for too long.

22:32.670 --> 22:34.000
Home is where the comfort is.

22:34.000 --> 22:34.730
Hear me out.

22:34.770 --> 22:35.630
You should go home.

22:35.670 --> 22:36.930
Don't make your family worry.

22:36.930 --> 22:39.070
Madam, give me another chance.

22:39.100 --> 22:40.600
I'll get the hang of it soon.

22:41.900 --> 22:43.730
My family wouldn't be worried.

22:43.730 --> 22:45.300
They couldn't wait to get rid of me.

22:52.100 --> 22:53.400
Be careful, okay?

23:13.930 --> 23:15.170
Did you send the letter?

23:16.570 --> 23:17.470
[Qingyu]
How are you?

23:18.100 --> 23:18.900
Where are you?

23:19.500 --> 23:20.830
Please reply.

23:42.070 --> 23:42.900
Hello?

23:43.870 --> 23:45.670
Around 3:00 AM today,

23:45.670 --> 23:47.370
this number called me.

23:47.900 --> 23:49.170
May I know who it was?

23:55.530 --> 23:56.270
Sir,

23:56.470 --> 23:57.670
we're not going to Nanqiao Village.

23:57.730 --> 23:58.630
Go to Huanzhou Terminal.

24:53.300 --> 24:54.170
Hello.

24:54.430 --> 24:54.800
Hello.

24:55.600 --> 24:57.300
[Missing Person]
Have you seen this girl?

24:57.700 --> 24:59.630
She is about this tall.

25:01.000 --> 25:01.330
Sir.

25:01.330 --> 25:02.070
Hello.

25:02.100 --> 25:05.400
Have you seen this girl?

25:07.000 --> 25:08.100
Have you seen this girl?

25:08.500 --> 25:09.600
Keep a copy.

25:09.600 --> 25:11.030
If you see her,

25:11.070 --> 25:12.300
please contact us.

25:12.300 --> 25:12.930
Sure.

25:12.930 --> 25:13.670
Thank you.

25:16.430 --> 25:17.370
Well?

25:19.230 --> 25:20.300
Over there.

25:20.530 --> 25:22.400
There is an information counter.
Ask the staff.

25:41.230 --> 25:42.230
Over here.

25:43.230 --> 25:44.600
See if this is her.

25:51.900 --> 25:53.200
Is this what you wanted?

25:53.400 --> 25:55.000
Working in a diner without a permit?

26:00.730 --> 26:01.500
What's wrong?

26:03.000 --> 26:04.000
Are you sick?

26:07.600 --> 26:08.730
I'd rather die here

26:08.770 --> 26:10.030
than go back.

26:10.200 --> 26:13.570
Qingyu, even if you hate them,

26:13.570 --> 26:15.200
this is not right.

26:15.470 --> 26:17.370
You've hurt everyone in the family.

26:18.300 --> 26:20.200
Come on. I'm bringing you home.

26:20.300 --> 26:21.330
I'm not going back.

26:21.470 --> 26:22.070
Come with me.

26:22.100 --> 26:22.770
The whole family...

26:22.770 --> 26:24.970
I don't want to go home!

26:26.670 --> 26:27.800
Don't you dare call my mother.

26:27.800 --> 26:29.200
Can you please stop messing around?

26:29.900 --> 26:31.830
Your dad rushed tirelessly
to Huanzhou yesterday.

26:32.000 --> 26:34.000
He went to every bus
and train station for you.

26:34.300 --> 26:35.730
Your grandpa and uncle are all here.

26:35.730 --> 26:36.830
They are worried for you.

26:36.870 --> 26:38.570
Are they really that worried?

26:38.770 --> 26:40.730
They want to bring me back
to interrogate me.

26:42.330 --> 26:43.500
Feihai.

26:43.800 --> 26:45.400
You saw the notes

26:45.430 --> 26:46.530
in the wedding sweets boxes.

26:47.200 --> 26:48.100
You know

26:48.100 --> 26:49.370
what Beiyu had to go through.

26:50.870 --> 26:52.470
Don't you pity her at all?

27:03.430 --> 27:04.800
But you are sick.

27:05.270 --> 27:06.270
Your grandma fainted

27:06.270 --> 27:07.300
at the wedding.

27:07.300 --> 27:08.730
She is still in the hospital.

27:08.730 --> 27:09.300
You should go home.

27:09.330 --> 27:10.700
I won't change my mind.

27:11.200 --> 27:12.800
And please, answer my question.

27:16.000 --> 27:17.770
Jinrui hurt my sister

27:17.770 --> 27:18.870
when she was in university.

27:20.900 --> 27:22.730
Don't you feel sorry for her?

27:23.270 --> 27:25.100
Jinrui's family
destroyed Beiyu's youth

27:25.530 --> 27:26.900
and her life.

27:26.900 --> 27:29.000
Don't you feel any resentment?

27:34.800 --> 27:36.000
Everyone makes mistakes.

27:38.500 --> 27:39.300
But the reality

27:39.330 --> 27:40.930
is that Beiyu is gone.

27:41.570 --> 27:43.370
Hating Jinrui won't change it.

27:44.430 --> 27:45.930
I wouldn't be as rash as you.

27:47.000 --> 27:47.800
Qingyu.

27:48.930 --> 27:51.270
This scandal is making waves,

27:51.430 --> 27:53.700
destroying years of reputation

27:53.930 --> 27:55.370
your family built.

27:55.400 --> 27:56.700
All those innocent people

27:57.000 --> 27:58.130
got caught up in this.

27:58.130 --> 27:58.670
Do you understand?

27:58.700 --> 28:00.230
No one is innocent.

28:00.900 --> 28:03.500
My grandparents, my uncle and his wife,

28:03.530 --> 28:04.730
and even my parents

28:04.730 --> 28:06.970
were covering up for Jinrui.

28:07.670 --> 28:09.730
To protect Jinrui,
they betrayed their conscience

28:09.730 --> 28:10.830
and smeared Beiyu.

28:11.070 --> 28:12.730
They were all part of this!

28:18.400 --> 28:19.730
Over the year,

28:21.070 --> 28:22.530
I've hated Qiao Beiyu.

28:24.130 --> 28:25.730
I used to think her actions

28:26.100 --> 28:27.600
were what caused trouble to our life.

28:29.070 --> 28:30.330
The innocent suffered mistreatment

28:30.330 --> 28:31.630
because of her.

28:33.570 --> 28:35.570
But when I learned what Jinrui had done,

28:37.430 --> 28:38.830
I realized

28:40.330 --> 28:42.970
that it wasn't Beiyu
who ruined our life.

28:46.200 --> 28:48.870
Those people drove her to a dead end.

28:51.500 --> 28:54.230
Beiyu used to be a cheerful person.

28:55.400 --> 28:56.200
Honestly,

28:56.930 --> 28:58.730
no one could tell
what she went through.

28:58.770 --> 29:01.030
Because she kept the pain to herself.

29:06.000 --> 29:06.770
Did you know

29:06.770 --> 29:08.170
she wrote about you in her diary?

29:10.470 --> 29:11.070
Did she...

29:13.800 --> 29:15.400
Did she call me

29:16.000 --> 29:17.830
weak and a coward?

29:18.570 --> 29:19.870
When she was hurt,

29:21.000 --> 29:22.430
I didn't stand up for her.

29:22.870 --> 29:23.570
On the contrary.

29:26.200 --> 29:27.770
You know what she wrote about you?

29:29.100 --> 29:30.130
Your kindness.

29:30.670 --> 29:31.400
Beiyu.

29:31.430 --> 29:34.030
It was the only glimpse of warmth
she had seen in many years.

29:54.270 --> 29:55.600
She was gone,

29:55.600 --> 29:58.300
yet we continued to shame her
with cruel and hurtful words.

29:58.770 --> 30:00.930
And then, we moved on with our lives

30:00.930 --> 30:02.200
as if nothing happened.

30:05.430 --> 30:07.300
This is not right.

30:08.700 --> 30:10.800
I don't regret telling the world
the truth of her past.

30:17.800 --> 30:18.900
Qingyu?

30:19.670 --> 30:21.730
Qingyu?

30:29.770 --> 30:31.000
Qingyu!

30:36.500 --> 30:37.400
Qingyu!

30:38.200 --> 30:40.000
You are still sick! Don't be rash!

30:40.000 --> 30:41.700
The rain and snow event is attributed

30:41.730 --> 30:42.970
to atmospheric circulation anomalies

30:43.000 --> 30:45.430
caused by the La Ni├▒a phenomenon.

30:45.770 --> 30:47.030
Since January,

30:47.070 --> 30:49.870
meridional atmospheric circulation
has led to cold air activities.

30:50.070 --> 30:52.370
As a result, over 20 provinces

30:52.400 --> 30:53.570
have been continuously affected.

32:06.130 --> 32:07.030
Beiyu.

32:09.100 --> 32:10.900
I've avenged you.

32:16.770 --> 32:19.170
But I still don't feel any relief.

32:20.930 --> 32:22.730
Instead, I feel way more burdened.

33:01.600 --> 33:05.470
ظآزPerhapsظآز

33:05.970 --> 33:11.630
ظآزThe more we care,
the more careful we becomeظآز

33:12.770 --> 33:18.170
ظآزCounting the distance that separates usظآز

33:18.970 --> 33:24.730
ظآزA single step, and we'd be closer stillظآز

33:30.300 --> 33:34.170
ظآزPerhapsظآز

33:34.870 --> 33:40.400
ظآزWe were afraid of losingظآز

33:41.570 --> 33:47.070
ظآزThat's why we were hesitantظآز

33:48.100 --> 33:53.530
ظآزBut you lingerظآز

33:56.400 --> 34:01.200
ظآزTurns out that what's on my mindظآز

34:02.100 --> 34:05.770
ظآزIs your nameظآز

34:06.230 --> 34:11.429
ظآزThe only stubbornness in my heartظآز

34:12.170 --> 34:15.570
ظآزAt first sightظآز

34:16.170 --> 34:19.300
ظآزThe future has been determinedظآز

34:20.100 --> 34:26.199
ظآزDreams began to feel realظآز

34:26.730 --> 34:30.500
ظآزTurns out that what's on your mindظآز

34:31.000 --> 34:35.000
ظآزIs a placeظآز

34:35.429 --> 34:40.730
ظآزWhere the same story is held dearظآز

34:41.500 --> 34:44.770
ظآزFortunately, I'm not sensible enoughظآز

34:45.300 --> 34:48.469
ظآزCourage wasn't late tooظآز

34:49.070 --> 34:55.170
ظآزOnly then does time
not betray our acquaintanceظآز

35:28.100 --> 35:29.700
It's 37.5 degrees. A mild fever.

35:30.130 --> 35:30.530
Qiao Dadan.

35:30.530 --> 35:31.930
Watch your temperature at home.

35:31.930 --> 35:32.670
If the fever goes on,

35:32.700 --> 35:33.800
take some fever medicine.

35:37.600 --> 35:38.530
Qiao Dadan?

35:39.170 --> 35:42.230
I knew you didn't
want your family to find you.

35:42.330 --> 35:44.270
So, I came up with an alias.

35:44.470 --> 35:46.300
Qiao Dadan, brave and bold
as the name implies.

35:49.270 --> 35:50.570
I thought you were abroad.

35:50.570 --> 35:51.800
When did you come back?

35:53.100 --> 35:54.700
Didn't I say so?

35:56.100 --> 35:57.800
I'll always stand by you.

36:04.430 --> 36:05.500
My son!

36:31.070 --> 36:32.170
What happened?

36:32.200 --> 36:34.400
A car crash on the city highway.

36:34.730 --> 36:35.970
It was a wedding ride,

36:36.130 --> 36:37.200
full of roses.

36:37.330 --> 36:39.630
I heard the couple were in bad shape.

36:39.670 --> 36:40.700
It was too gruesome.

36:41.470 --> 36:44.030
How poor.
A car crash on their wedding day?

36:44.070 --> 36:44.930
Yeah.

36:45.400 --> 36:46.700
I hope they are all right.

36:48.100 --> 36:48.900
Excuse me...

36:50.670 --> 36:51.130
Nurse!

36:51.130 --> 36:52.500
We need help now!

36:53.270 --> 36:54.200
What happened?

36:54.570 --> 36:55.700
She passed out.

36:55.900 --> 36:57.030
Help us!

36:59.730 --> 37:00.430
What's wrong?

37:00.800 --> 37:01.500
She passed out.

37:03.730 --> 37:04.970
She just lost consciousness.

37:05.730 --> 37:06.970
Put her down. Slowly.

37:07.000 --> 37:07.600
Madam?

37:16.530 --> 37:18.000
Did I make a mistake?

37:20.070 --> 37:21.570
I don't think it's a mistake.

37:23.130 --> 37:24.030
But why?

37:24.100 --> 37:25.730
Why do I feel so much fear

37:26.530 --> 37:28.330
after doing the right thing?

37:29.470 --> 37:30.900
You said you were fearless.

37:37.930 --> 37:40.030
I used to think so.

37:41.130 --> 37:42.770
Then I did it,

37:44.270 --> 37:46.200
and realized just how timid I am.

37:46.870 --> 37:48.470
I couldn't go to the wedding.

37:48.530 --> 37:49.900
I was worried my grandpa and uncle

37:49.900 --> 37:51.200
would go after my parents.

37:52.170 --> 37:53.570
What if Jinrui and Xiaoyun

37:53.570 --> 37:55.000
were in the operation theater?

37:56.000 --> 37:56.900
What should I do?

38:04.800 --> 38:05.870
Stop being paranoid.

38:06.430 --> 38:07.930
Focus on getting better

38:08.000 --> 38:08.500
for now.

38:14.170 --> 38:16.370
Could you lend me some money?

38:22.000 --> 38:23.800
Money won't do you any good.

38:24.700 --> 38:26.100
As soon as you go out,

38:26.730 --> 38:28.130
you have nowhere to go.

38:29.970 --> 38:30.830
Your parents

38:30.830 --> 38:32.530
posted the missing person notice
in the newspaper.

38:33.430 --> 38:35.130
You just made the headline.

38:39.900 --> 38:41.170
Forget it.

38:41.300 --> 38:42.830
Just lend me some money.

38:42.870 --> 38:44.500
I can't just leave you be.

38:44.700 --> 38:45.730
I didn't come back from abroad

38:45.730 --> 38:46.830
just to do nothing.

38:53.570 --> 38:54.830
I know a place

38:55.430 --> 38:57.000
where your parents won't find you.

38:57.270 --> 38:57.870
Come with me.

39:34.000 --> 39:34.900
Madam Ma.

39:36.170 --> 39:37.030
The goods are here.

39:37.130 --> 39:38.370
You're early today.

39:38.400 --> 39:39.430
I have to.

39:40.070 --> 39:41.200
I can handle it.

39:41.570 --> 39:42.700
Do you still feel cold?

39:46.670 --> 39:47.200
Over here.

40:02.870 --> 40:04.500
I think it's hurt.

40:05.300 --> 40:05.700
Yeah.

40:25.070 --> 40:26.770
This birdcage belonged to my grandpa.

40:27.430 --> 40:30.200
I didn't expect
it'd come in handy someday.

40:33.600 --> 40:34.630
Your family has searched

40:34.670 --> 40:36.000
every corner of Huanzhou.

40:36.300 --> 40:37.400
They will never suspect

40:37.430 --> 40:39.200
you're hiding right under their noses.

40:39.430 --> 40:40.700
Therefore, the most risky place

40:40.700 --> 40:41.900
turns out

40:42.200 --> 40:43.500
to be the safest.

40:54.530 --> 40:55.100
It's chilly outside.

40:55.100 --> 40:56.530
Do you want to take a hot shower?

40:56.530 --> 40:57.400
It'll make you warmer.

40:59.230 --> 41:00.870
I didn't bring any clothes.

41:01.070 --> 41:02.900
It's fine. You can wear mine.

41:04.500 --> 41:05.830
They're all washed.

41:06.270 --> 41:07.030
They're clean.

41:07.470 --> 41:08.330
Don't worry.

41:13.370 --> 41:14.370
You're not thinking anything weird,
are you?

41:47.000 --> 41:50.670
ظآزPerhapsظآز

