ظآزIn the futureظآز

42:19.800 --> 42:25.500
ظآزTime will reveal this secretظآز

42:27.030 --> 42:32.100
ظآزWaiting is a silent promiseظآز

42:33.330 --> 42:38.470
ظآزThat never expiresظآز

42:42.100 --> 42:46.570
ظآزTurns out that what's on my mindظآز

42:47.570 --> 42:51.230
ظآزIs your nameظآز

